subsection.p:
          The following example shows drag 'n drop between two JLists named
          "source" and "destination"
          
dialog.list("source").drag("Swing");
dialog.list("destination").drop("AWT");

          The following example shows drag 'n drop between two JTabless named
          "source" and "destination"
          
// import static org.fest.swing.fixture.TableCell.TableCellBuilder.row;          
dialog.table("source").drag(row(3).column(0));
dialog.table("destination").drop(row(1).column(0));

          The following example shows drag 'n drop between two JTreess named
          "source" and "destination"
          
dialog.tree("source").drag(path("root", "branch1", "branch1.1"));
dialog.tree("destination").drop(path("root"));
